lead_paragraph: In the first such high-level visit in nearly a decade, Sameh Shoukry, Egypt’s foreign minister, arrived in Israel to help rejuvenate the moribund peace process.

headline.print_headline: A Top Egyptian, in Israel, Pushes for Regional Peace
headline.main: Egyptian Minister Visits Israel in Push for Peace With Palestinians

snippet: In the first such high-level visit in nearly a decade, Sameh Shoukry, Egypt’s foreign minister, arrived in Israel to help rejuvenate the moribund peace process....
abstract: Egypt's foreign minister Sameh Shoukry arrives in Israel in hopes of reinvigorating stalled Israeli-Palestinian peace process.
